methods.makeLocation:
Manufacture a TableLocation from the supplied key

:param tableKey: (TableLocationFactory.TK) - The TableKey for the provider using this factory
:param locationKey: (TableLocationFactory.TLK) - The TableLocationKey (or an immutable equivalent) returned by a paired
        TableLocationKeyFinder
:param refreshService: (io.deephaven.engine.table.impl.locations.util.TableDataRefreshService) - An optional TableDataRefreshService, non-null if the enclosing provider
        supports subscriptions
:return: (io.deephaven.engine.table.impl.locations.TableLocation) A new or cached TableLocation identified by the supplied TableKey and
         TableLocationKey
